OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government must do more to recover 
OL,6, taxes that went unpaid during the      
OL,7, pandemic, a group of MPs has said.     
OL,9,FThe Public Accounts Committee said the 
OL,10,Ftotal UK tax debt was #39bn - more than
OL,11,Fdouble the amount at the start of 2020.
OL,13,FIt said HM Revenue and Customs must    
OL,14,Fpursue businesses and individuals who  
OL,15,Fwere choosing not to pay their taxes   
OL,16,Fwhile supporting those still struggling
OL,17,Fwith the impact of the pandemic.       
OL,19,FHMRC said it was recouping debts and   
OL,20,Fwould also be recruiting more staff.   
